Evil Never Dies was released on Nuclear War Now Prods and Witches Brew Records 20 years ago this Fall. Hard to believe it’s been that long!

Something no one really knows about outside of Yosuke from NWN is that Evil Never Dies was recorded twice. There’s a whole separate recording that has never seen the light of day. What do you think about a double LP release that includes that original recording?
